context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24945,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/06\/05\/fast-ramadan-sins-forgiven\/","url_meta":{"origin":3705,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Whoever fasts Ramadan will have his sins forgiven","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 5, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdur Rahman ibn Awf reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Ramadan is a month in which Allah Almighty has obligated its fasting. I have instituted for Muslims the practice of prayer at night. Thus, whoever fasts it with faith and expecting reward will\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14956,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/14\/last-ten-nights-ramadan\/","url_meta":{"origin":3705,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Laylat al-Qadr in last ten nights of Ramadan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 14, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSearch for the Night of Decree in the odd nights among the last ten nights of Ramadan.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2017, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1169 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":4385,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/07\/hadith-on-itikaf-ramadan\/","url_meta":{"origin":3705,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on I&#8217;tikaf: The Prophet&#8217;s spiritual retreat in Ramadan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 7, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would seek spiritual retreat in the mosque\u00a0during the last ten nights of Ramadan, until Allah Almighty caused him to pass away. His wives continued to perform the retreat after him. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2026, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1172 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":4389,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/08\/laylat-al-qadar-seven-nights\/","url_meta":{"origin":3705,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Laylat al-Qadr in last seven nights of Ramadan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 8, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cLook for the Night of Decree in the last ten nights of Ramadan. If one of you is weak or unable, then do not be overcome by the remaining seven nights.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1165 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2010\/09\/18\/prayer-fasting-ramadan-friday\/","url_meta":{"origin":3705,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Redemption: Prayer and fasting expiate minor sins","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 18, 2010","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira\u00a0reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe five prayers, Friday to Friday, and Ramadan to Ramadan will expiate the sins committed between them, as long as major sins are avoided.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 233 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3705","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3705"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3705\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[